= Session Management

Created by Sandip Ransing Nov 2009. 

Session Management allows us to track user information 

Each site has its own independent sitemap/page-tree and these attributes:

== Installation

1) Unpack/checkout/export the extension into vendor/extensions of your 
   project.

2) Run the extension update task.

  $ rake production radiant:extensions:session_management:update

3) Restart your server

== Acknowledgments

Thanks to Localc car site, for inspiring me to write this extension